1
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:41,560
Sir. Parents are gathering out there.

2
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,280
It's been 22 days!

3
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,440
My son, Hong Jinyang,

4
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:56,600
is still nowhere to be seen!

5
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,400
I only have one child.

6
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:03,360
What am I going to do
if something happens to him?

7
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,320
My son…

8
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,240
It has been…

9
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,240
Officer!

10
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:10,080
- Officer.
- Where is my child?

11
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:11,840
Please. Officer!

12
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,640
Don't do that.

13
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,640
Please.

14
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:15,040
- Find my child.
- Everyone.

15
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,040
Everyone. Please calm down.

16
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,680
We are as anxious as you.

17
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:21,080
We haven't slept for a few days.

18
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:24,960
Creating a ruckus here
is not going to solve the problem, is it?

19
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,600
- Go. Tear it down.
- Okay.

20
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,480
- No! Don't!
- Who dares to tear it down!

21
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,520
No!

22
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,080
Who said you could tear it down?

23
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:39,760
Keep the posters up.

24
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,120
Will tearing the posters down
solve the problem?

25
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,960
Will it locate the children?

26
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:49,400
Citizens can post whatever they want.

27
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,920
Use your expertise

28
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,320
if you want to bring the posters down.

29
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,040
My fellow parents.

30
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,280
I am Zhao Jie,

31
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,320
Captain of the Criminal Department
in Nanshan Branch.

32
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:11,440
Today, I will give you my word

33
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,440
that within seven days,

34
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:16,480
we will solve the case
and give you an answer.

35
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,360
If we fail to do so,

36
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,280
I will step down.

37
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,600
I'll take your word for it.

38
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,560
Thank you so much!

39
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:28,160
- No need to do this.
- Please.

40
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,520
Thank you.

41
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:36,160
MISSING PERSON

42
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,680
WEIYANG PUBLIC
SECURITY BUREAU NANSHAN BRANCH

43
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,440
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

44
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,520
MISSING PERSONS SPECIAL TASK FORCE

45
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,280
We have questioned everyone
from the illegal internet cafe

46
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,480
in Yuanlongli.

47
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:54,000
None of the 18 are under suspicion.

48
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:59,080
All five teenagers went missing
after they skipped classes.

49
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,760
Three of them

50
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,800
last appeared
at the illegal internet cafe.

51
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,520
The victims don't know each other.

52
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,640
They couldn't possibly have

53
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:07,840
planned together to go
missing voluntarily.

54
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,280
One of them was injured

55
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,080
and is currently traumatized.

56
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:14,280
We can basically conclude
that it's a serial kidnapping case.

57
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,880
Captain Zhao made a promise yesterday.

58
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:19,000
We only have seven days.

59
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,440
We must find

60
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,640
these kids within seven days,
even if we have

61
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,600
to turn the entire city upside down.

62
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,360
Good. Speak.

63
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:28,000
Captain Qu. If this is the doing
of a serial kidnapper,

64
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:31,160
can we release a statement to the school

65
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:34,080
clarifying that Han Zi'ang
is the victim of the kidnapping,

66
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,480
and he only attacked someone
out of fear and shock?

67
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,880
You there.

68
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,720
Handle this matter.

69
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,640
Yes, sir!

70
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,680
Let's circle back.

71
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:50,680
Captain Zhao wants us
to submit a new investigation plan.

72
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,320
Let's work together and brainstorm.

73
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,920
You can still take more pawns.

74
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,560
- Dad.
- That's right.

75
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,760
Hey.

76
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,040
So?

77
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,600
Got your assignment?

78
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:15,480
Nothing.

79
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,720
Other than a few side-eyes.

80
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:22,000
Qu Dahai doesn't have
what it takes to solve cases.

81
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:24,600
He learned a few tricks from Ran
and began to show off.

82
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,520
Sooner or later,
he'll lead the case to a dead end.

83
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,280
We're having an emergency.

84
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,560
Stop saying something unhelpful.

85
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:34,200
But Ran's theory is still useful.

86
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,400
Everything has a center.

87
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,640
And outside the center,
there will be ripples.

88
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:42,080
Dad. I've read the book thrice.

89
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,600
What are you getting at?

90
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:52,040
CHAPTER 2: "EYE OF THE VORTEX THEORY"

91
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,280
To see the eye of the vortex,

92
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,160
you must be part of it.

93
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,640
The Eye of the Vortex Theory.

94
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,480
Officer He,

95
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,920
I don't know anything
about investigations.

96
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,960
But allow me to thank you
on behalf of the school.

97
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,680
If you hadn't defended

98
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,520
Han Zi'ang this relentlessly,

99
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:21,080
this turn of events
wouldn't have occurred at all.

100
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:24,640
Right now, the students
and the parents no longer view Han Zi'ang

101
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,000
as a problematic student,

102
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,560
but as a hero who fought
against the kidnapper.

103
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,000
Principal Qin.

104
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,640
I still need your help
to identify the culprit.

105
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,920
Me?

106
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,560
DANFENG MIDDLE SCHOOL

107
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,640
Class, stand!

108
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:14,600
- Good morning, sir.
- Sit down.

109
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,760
Open your geometry textbooks.

110
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:19,040
<i>Let's have a recap</i>
<i>of what we learned previously.</i>

111
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:25,280
Bye, sir.

112
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,760
Bye.

113
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,680
Miss, are you role-playing as Han Zi'ang?

114
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:35,960
Yes.

115
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,600
He isn't as spirited as you are.

116
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,520
He spends half of his day sleeping.

117
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,320
Then what does he do
for the rest of his day?

118
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,720
Reading comics. His mind
lives in another dimension.

119
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,920
Xuan. Over here.

120
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,920
Han Zi'ang is a weirdo, right?

121
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,480
Yes. We can't understand
what he says at all.

122
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,640
I think he's obsessed with a cosplayer.

123
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,880
He even said he'd attend
a comic convention

124
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,240
in Shanghai during summer break.

125
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,800
No need to search online.
His interest has changed.

126
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:01,520
He is now a fan of an anime.

127
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:05,240
Right. He loves… What is she called again?

128
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,400
Nangong…

129
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:09,000
This one here.

130
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,200
Yes! Nangong Xuanyue.

131
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:16,120
NANGONG XUANYUE

132
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:21,760
TOGETHER FOR YOUR HEALTH
UNITED IN TRUST AND CARE

133
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,960
Drink some water.

134
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:34,240
Everyone at school
knows you're the victim.

135
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,799
Principal Qin said you were very brave.

136
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:38,799
They are looking forward to your return.

137
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,039
Ang.

138
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,919
Do you hear me?

139
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,720
Xuanyue.

140
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,760
You've come back.

141
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,320
He Xiaohe!

142
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,840
- Calm down.
- He Xiaohe!

143
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,040
- He Xiaohe!
- You can't go in.

144
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,840
- You can't enter.
- Let me.

145
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,800
You can't enter.
There's no one else inside.

146
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,400
We've brought everyone out.

147
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,320
Please calm down.
We've brought everyone out.

148
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,880
POLICE

149
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,320
Uncle Ran.

150
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,560
Are you injured?

151
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,160
Keyboard!

152
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,400
Keyboard…

153
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:20,520
Where were you?

154
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,040
Hey!

155
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:23,960
She was at my place.

156
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,440
Who are you?

157
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,120
Why was she at your place?
What did you do to her?

158
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,800
- She clung to me!
- Tell me!

159
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,440
- What did you do to her?
- Stop!

160
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,480
- Let go!
- Do you know how old she is?

161
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:34,600
Let go…

162
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,360
What is wrong with you?

163
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,560
- He's my friend, not a criminal!
- Come.

164
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:39,760
Come back with me.

165
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:43,320
- Come!
- No! Let go of me!

166
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,920
I won't come back with you.

167
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,520
You don't even know what happened.

168
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,080
Don't just assume everything.

169
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:50,360
So much for thinking
you are my best friend!

170
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,240
Xiaohe!

171
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,720
Double Stripe.

172
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:08,240
You peed here last time.

173
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,760
I've held a lot this time. Let's compete.

174
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:13,840
- You? Maybe after you beat Bunny first.
- Come.

175
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,360
Come.

176
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,280
Ready.

177
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,760
Three.

178
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,360
Two.

179
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,800
Why did you shout?

180
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:28,680
What is that?

181
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,160
What…

182
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,600
It… It might be a person.

183
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:38,880
It is a person.

184
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,680
I've never met her.

185
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:02,320
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

186
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,280
- Hurry up.
- Hurry.

187
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,360
Open the shutter.

188
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,400
Open it.

189
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:34,840
Put her in here.

190
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:39,080
JIAJIA GROCERY

191
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:41,440
Mister, we found a frozen girl.

192
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,960
Bring her inside.
Don't freeze her to death.

193
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:46,880
- Come.
- Fine.

194
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,480
One, two, three.

195
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,680
Let's go.

196
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,000
Careful.

197
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,360
Careful.

198
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,120
Careful.

199
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:03,360
TUNZHOU CITY

200
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,520
TUNZHOU LOCAL FAVORITES

201
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:09,920
Mister.

202
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:12,840
- A bowl of noodles, please.
- Sure. Please go inside.

203
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,600
Enjoy. Careful. It's hot.

204
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:37,400
Mister,

205
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,920
do you know

206
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:43,600
any unique places in Tunzhou,

207
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:46,600
or maybe a place
photographers love to visit?

208
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,360
There are plenty of them.

209
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,280
Look.

210
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,880
We have Yongji Bridge,

211
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,640
Sanyi Temple, Zhang Fei's Shrine,

212
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:55,280
and this, Tunzhou Twin Towers.

213
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:58,640
- Mister. Can I have some pepper?
- Sure.

214
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:01,760
YONGJI BRIDGE
SANYI TEMPLE, ZHANG FEI'S SHRINE

215
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,400
Mister.

216
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:22,600
Any place that is quite desolate?

217
00:14:22,680 --> 00:14:24,320
A place that has been abandoned for years.

218
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,320
What a peculiar preference.

219
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,200
Here.

220
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:32,840
This one here?

221
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:35,720
COPPER FACTORY

222
00:14:38,640 --> 00:14:39,960
Copper Factory.

223
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:49,040
JIAJIA GROCERY

224
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,640
CONVENIENT AND AFFORDABLE

225
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,960
Send in the soldiers.

226
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,640
Bunny.

227
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,880
This girl is so fierce.

228
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,680
Wake up!

229
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,440
You…

230
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:32,880
Who are you? Who the heck are you?

231
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,640
- Who are you?
- Help!

232
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,040
Who are you?

233
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,480
Stop hitting him. Stop hitting him.

234
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,560
- Get her!
- Bring it on!

235
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,280
Bring it on!

236
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:48,600
Don't try to mess with me.

237
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,720
Stop!

238
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,480
Don't come any closer!

239
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,720
<i>Hello?</i>

240
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,840
Hello, Dad.

241
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,400
Xiaohe.

242
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,640
Where are you calling me from?

243
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:26,280
The shop by the school's gate.

244
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,400
It's so late now.

245
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:29,480
Why aren't you at school?

246
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,880
Why are you calling me?

247
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,560
Nothing.

248
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:39,480
Then I'll hang up now.

249
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:41,320
<i>My phone is dying.</i>

250
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,680
<i>Go back to your class.</i>

251
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:45,000
Finish your homework and eat on time.

252
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,520
Listen to Uncle Ran.

253
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:48,200
<i>Do you hear me?</i>

254
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,480
Hello?

255
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:52,600
Hello?

256
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,240
She's skipping classes again.

257
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:07,119
<i>Keyboard. You're gone.</i>

258
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,599
<i>The band is gone.</i>

259
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,839
<i>No one at home cares about me.</i>

260
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:12,560
<i>Where should I go now?</i>

261
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:20,680
<i>If you really want to learn music,</i>
<i>you can go to Beijing.</i>

262
00:17:23,839 --> 00:17:25,200
Go home now.

263
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:28,280
This place is not an orphanage.

264
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:29,880
Exactly.

265
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:39,440
Please don't kick me out.

266
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:40,520
My dad…

267
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:42,800
I was adopted.

268
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:45,240
My dad hits me every day
and forces me to drop out of school.

269
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,000
I'm too scared to go home.

270
00:17:47,080 --> 00:17:49,120
I want to work

271
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,920
to pay for my tuition.

272
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,200
What a rough childhood.

273
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:55,800
No wonder she's so violent.

274
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,920
Mister, help her out.

275
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,320
She has to work to fund her studies.

276
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,960
That's already tough enough.

277
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:06,440
Mister, let me help you in your shop.

278
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:08,120
I only have one rule.

279
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:10,640
The internet cafe
downstairs is unlicensed.

280
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:12,160
So don't mess it up for me.

281
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,720
You must be Wan Qiming.

282
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,000
POLICE

283
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,960
So, you found me after all.

284
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,520
I met her through a magazine.

285
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,240
We were pen pals.

286
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:02,560
We wrote more than
ten letters to each other.

287
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,840
We had feelings for each other.

288
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,360
So, we decided to meet up.

289
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,320
It became official then.

290
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:13,040
I began to look for a job in Weiyang.

291
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,960
She's a bit color-blind.

292
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:26,160
So I only took monochrome photos of her.

293
00:19:26,240 --> 00:19:28,800
As time went by, it became a habit.

294
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,200
I don't take colored photos anymore.

295
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,840
Around three months after we met,

296
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,080
she brought me home.

297
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:37,480
Her relatives were quite fond of me.

298
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:40,160
Her father was eccentric,

299
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,480
but he didn't say no to it.

300
00:19:42,360 --> 00:19:43,920
Everything was going so well.

301
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,800
Qiming.

302
00:20:01,280 --> 00:20:02,440
Let's get married.

303
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,240
Meng.

304
00:20:11,760 --> 00:20:14,280
Come with me to Guangdong.

305
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:17,280
I'd love to marry you,

306
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,480
but I don't have a career now.

307
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:20,840
Weiyang is too small.

308
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:23,360
I don't want to stay here
doing wedding photography forever.

309
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,920
Let's work hard for a few years.

310
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:28,280
Once our careers are stable,
we'll get married.

311
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:32,880
What's the matter?

312
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:37,120
I don't want a career.

313
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:41,320
I just want a family.

314
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,960
But we're still young.

315
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:51,080
We can prove ourselves.

316
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,800
- Do you know that--
- Qiming.

317
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:56,000
I can't leave my dad.

318
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,200
Can you stay in Weiyang?

319
00:21:10,240 --> 00:21:12,920
<i>In the end, I decided</i>
<i>to head to Guangdong.</i>

320
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:15,360
We separated

321
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,480
and resumed our written communication,
as we did before.

322
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:21,200
Then she said she'd wait for me,

323
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:24,760
that once I earned enough money,
I'd return to Weiyang to marry her.

324
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:26,640
I said yes.

325
00:21:28,080 --> 00:21:29,320
And then?

326
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:33,000
After more than six months,
she stopped replying to my letters.

327
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,080
I called her home,
but no one would pick up.

328
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,320
<i>During the Qingming Festival of 1996,</i>

329
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,720
<i>I told my mentor</i>

330
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,480
<i>that I wanted to return home</i>
<i>to pay respect to my ancestors.</i>

331
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:42,920
<i>But in fact, I went</i>
<i>to Weiyang to look for her.</i>

332
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:29,400
That's when I learned

333
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,320
that she and her father
were in the accident at Mount Wu.

334
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:36,320
To treat her dad, she took out loans.

335
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,680
But what I couldn't accept

336
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:42,400
was that Xu Zhihong
forced his daughter to…

337
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,840
For his medical bill.

338
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,200
Meng.

339
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,680
Come with me.

340
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:12,320
Let's go to Guangdong.

341
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:18,800
Just leave.

342
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:24,480
I don't mind what you used to do.

343
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,360
My career is blooming right now.

344
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,600
We'll get married
once we arrive in Guangdong.

345
00:23:30,520 --> 00:23:32,920
We'll build a family. Okay?

346
00:23:34,320 --> 00:23:35,600
Please?

347
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:40,560
I gave you a chance back then.

348
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:43,000
Now, there's no way I can leave Weiyang.

349
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,560
Why do you want

350
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:48,480
to stay in this broken home of yours?

351
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,920
My dad is back. Go inside.

352
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,600
Go inside.

353
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:04,560
You jerk.

354
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,880
You dumped Meng and ran away.

355
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:10,000
I knew you were not a good man.

356
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:11,480
Why are you back?

357
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:14,760
What do you want?
To lure her away with your lies again?

358
00:24:14,840 --> 00:24:17,000
Dad. He came back to visit me.
He'll leave soon.

359
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,280
- Move aside!
- He'll leave soon.

360
00:24:18,360 --> 00:24:19,680
Bugger off!

361
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:24,440
Bugger off! Bugger off! Bugger off!

362
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:25,960
Do not touch me!

363
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:27,480
You're a father.

364
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:30,000
Yet you forced your daughter
to sell her body.

365
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:31,640
What kind of man are you?

366
00:24:32,160 --> 00:24:33,680
Who are you to judge me?

367
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:37,240
This is my home. I have the final say.

368
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:40,080
As long as I still live,

369
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,640
you will not take Meng away.

370
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,560
Dad, sit down.

371
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:46,160
- Bugger off!
- Dad.

372
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,920
Just go! Dad.

373
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,680
I wasn't willing to let it go initially,

374
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:56,200
so I hired the neighbor
opposite them to spy on them

375
00:24:57,840 --> 00:25:00,000
and see what's going on every day.

376
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:03,400
Actually, I was hoping
that the old man would die soon.

377
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,720
What did your informant tell you?

378
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,320
Nothing in particular.

379
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,320
Just that she kept working

380
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,200
in that line of work.

381
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,320
If one place was busted,

382
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,240
she would find another.

383
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:21,160
And then?

384
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:25,000
Then, a few months ago, I saw the news

385
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:26,720
that her father had died.

386
00:25:35,360 --> 00:25:38,520
Xu Zhihong was a selfish man.

387
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:40,800
Did he not deserve death?

388
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,480
Did he not deserve to be killed?

389
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,640
Do you think Xu Meng is dead?

390
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,560
I'm not sure about that.

391
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:57,320
But when we were pen pals, I had a hunch

392
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:59,520
that she had other pen pals.

393
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,800
She is the kind of girl
who likes to be doted on.

394
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,240
She has a temper.

395
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:07,160
She is prideful.

396
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:10,520
Girls like her, in that line of work,

397
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:12,560
will offend a lot of people.

398
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:16,840
Mr. Officer, I've told you
everything I can.

399
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:20,360
I didn't kill Xu Zhihong.

400
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,480
And I'd never hurt Xu Meng.

401
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,520
Xu Meng and her father

402
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:29,200
went missing the day before
the Hong Kong handover.

403
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:32,280
My mentor took a gig back then

404
00:26:32,800 --> 00:26:34,120
and brought me to Hong Kong to shoot

405
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,080
the lives of the Hong Kong citizens
before the reunification.

406
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:38,760
I was already away by the middle of June.

407
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:44,120
I have an alibi.

408
00:26:55,840 --> 00:26:56,840
Zhao Jie.

409
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,240
I was looking for you.

410
00:26:58,320 --> 00:27:00,240
This is the department's
annual budget. Please sign it.

411
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:02,040
I'm here to report a case.

412
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:05,520
He Xiaohe, resident of Unit 401,
Block 7, Ward 12, Poluo Street,

413
00:27:05,600 --> 00:27:07,320
13 years old, might have gone missing.

414
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:09,200
I thought it was something serious.

415
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,760
- That's just Xiaohe being Xiaohe.
- Exactly.

416
00:27:10,840 --> 00:27:12,600
She runs away every few days.

417
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,800
Okay. Report received.

418
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,760
- Chen. Register it right away.
- Okay.

419
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:25,960
Before she went missing, she was with me.

420
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:28,200
A good friend of hers
died in a fire in the bar.

421
00:27:28,280 --> 00:27:29,920
She is probably traumatized.

422
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,920
I've heard about it.

423
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,600
The victim was locked in the storeroom.

424
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,280
Someone next door didn't
extinguish their cigarette properly,

425
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,520
and it fell on the carpet.

426
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,000
The fire burned everything.

427
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,800
The victim was called Keyboard.

428
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:40,920
I knew him too.

429
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:48,200
Check every location on this list.

430
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:49,360
Mobilize the officers
with Mangkun as soon as possible.

431
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,360
Okay.

432
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:51,760
Here. Take a look.

433
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:53,680
Chen, have you registered the case?

434
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:55,280
The important information is in it.

435
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:57,040
- Have you seen this girl?
- No.

436
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,600
Take a look. Have you seen this girl?

437
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,320
- Let me see.
- Take a look.

438
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:02,040
She's this tall. Around 13 years old.

439
00:28:02,120 --> 00:28:03,280
DRUMS, PERCUSSION

440
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:07,280
Sir, this is
the security footage for today.

441
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:08,200
Can you fast forward it?

442
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,000
- Sure.
- Fast forward it.

443
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:10,720
Let me skim through it.

444
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:11,720
SUNDAY

445
00:28:14,040 --> 00:28:15,120
WEIYANG PARK, WEIYANG SQUARE
NANSHAN SUPERMARKET, WEIYANG BOOK STORE…

446
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,440
WEIYANG TRAIN STATION

447
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:30,360
CALLS

448
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:31,440
MENTOR

449
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:34,280
<i>The number you're dialing</i>
<i>has been switched off.</i>

450
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:35,760
<i>Please try again later.</i>

451
00:28:36,440 --> 00:28:37,880
END CALL

452
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:39,600
POLICE

453
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,040
- Check inside.
- Okay.

454
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,080
WEIYANG BUS TERMINAL

455
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,400
Don't mind me.

456
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,720
WEIYANG BUS TERMINAL

457
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,120
RIVERSIDE MARKET

458
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:15,160
How am I supposed to go back to Ran now?

459
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,360
It's so cold now.

460
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:19,880
Where could she have gone?

461
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:25,360
She has always been
a hyperactive troublemaker.

462
00:29:25,960 --> 00:29:27,760
I'm sure she's fine.

463
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:32,640
JIAJIA GROCERY

464
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:45,680
CHINESE CHESS

465
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,400
See you.

466
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:54,480
Come back again.

467
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,800
Thank you.

468
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,800
Little girl, do you have cigarettes here?

469
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:15,800
No. Only snacks and drinks.

470
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:18,440
Can you get me two soft packs of Yuxi?

471
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:19,920
You can keep the change.

472
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:29,280
Yuxi is 21 yuan a pack.

473
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:30,560
This is a huge deal.

474
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,440
Thank you, mister.
I'll get your cigarettes now.

475
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:36,880
- Look after this for me.
- Okay.

476
00:30:37,840 --> 00:30:39,040
ROUTE 36 TRAIN STATION TO MALL STREET

477
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,240
Keyboard.

478
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:22,880
How are you on the other side?

479
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:26,960
<i>Make sure you're practicing there too.</i>

480
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:31,600
<i>You will be the best keyboardist ever.</i>

481
00:31:34,840 --> 00:31:35,920
Also,

482
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:38,200
don't be a chicken.

483
00:31:39,360 --> 00:31:40,560
You'll get bullied like this.

484
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:58,880
POLICE

485
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,760
MOUNT WU TOURIST AREA

486
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:29,160
A three-day trip to Mount Wu.

487
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,920
Come take a look.

488
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,480
It's our new offer.

489
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:34,400
Have you heard of it?

490
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:36,240
Sir. Sir.

491
00:32:36,320 --> 00:32:37,880
New offer, new promotion.

492
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,040
Come take a look.

493
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,600
New offer, new promotion.

494
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:44,360
- Do you go to the train station?
- Come in.

495
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:47,000
Sir!

496
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,480
Sir. It has been a few tough years.

497
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:50,720
Give me a chance. Take a look.

498
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,000
Thank you.

499
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:57,040
KUNPENG TRAVEL AGENCY

500
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,360
We have a new offer.

501
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:00,360
Sorry.

502
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,960
New offer, new promotion.

503
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,520
Coming!

504
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:10,520
When is the next departure date?

505
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,440
Which one?

506
00:33:12,040 --> 00:33:13,520
The three-day Mount Wu trip.

507
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:14,600
KUNPENG TRAVEL AGENCY, MOUNT WU TOUR
FRIDAY DEPARTURES, 3-DAY TRIP

508
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:20,440
JIAJIA GROCERY

509
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:24,520
I bought you an egg each.
Come get your nutrition.

510
00:33:26,960 --> 00:33:28,600
You've worked so hard.

511
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,960
Have you earned enough
for your tuition fee?

512
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:35,640
Truth be told,

513
00:33:36,320 --> 00:33:37,600
I'm trying

514
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:39,520
to save for my train ticket to Beijing.

515
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:41,240
To Beijing?

516
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,440
Are you going there
to study at Tsinghua University?

517
00:33:43,520 --> 00:33:44,640
Little girl.

518
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,560
The usual, please.

519
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:47,640
You can keep the change.

520
00:33:49,120 --> 00:33:49,960
Thank you, mister.

521
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:52,120
Wait.

522
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:53,800
The beer is on me.

523
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:58,640
I'm a Buddhist. I don't drink.

524
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,760
Thank you, though.

525
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:05,360
SPICY CHICKEN BITES
WITH SECRET FAMILY RECIPE

526
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:23,040
Sorry.

527
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:26,679
He Xiaohe. Is that a cigarette pack I see?

528
00:34:29,239 --> 00:34:30,159
Stay right there!

529
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:34,800
Stay right there!

530
00:34:39,159 --> 00:34:40,440
He Xiaohe. Stay right there.

531
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:41,120
YUXI CIGARETTE

532
00:34:41,199 --> 00:34:42,840
She can run.

533
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:44,520
Stay right there.

534
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,320
Stop. Stay right there.

535
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:50,440
Stop.

536
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,440
He Xiaohe. Stop.

537
00:34:57,520 --> 00:34:59,320
You really can run.

538
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:21,600
Let's see where you can go now.

539
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,240
I'll stay.

540
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:43,960
- Bye, sir.
- You…

541
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:54,400
1.4 meters. This tall.

542
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,440
Take a look.

543
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:01,120
Mister.

544
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,280
Zhao Jie.

545
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,160
Captain Ran. Qu.

546
00:36:12,560 --> 00:36:14,760
It was very cold that night.
She couldn't have run far.

547
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:17,200
Focus on the 24-hour shops

548
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,840
within the red circles.

549
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:20,880
Let's split up and search.

550
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:21,920
It'll be more efficient.

551
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:23,480
Mangkun, Chen. You guys go here.

552
00:36:23,560 --> 00:36:24,680
I'll take this one. Okay?

553
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:26,280
- Okay.
- Split the workload among yourselves.

554
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,120
Hi, Mr. Zhang.

555
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,160
Hello?

556
00:36:29,240 --> 00:36:30,880
Are you the parent of He Xiaohe?

557
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:32,920
She didn't come to class today.

558
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:35,520
I saw her running around with cigarettes.
Will you please discipline her?

559
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:38,400
When? Where did you see her?

560
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,880
Tell me more.

561
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,400
I see.

562
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,680
Forgive me, Mr. Zhang.

563
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,960
I'll lecture her later.

564
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:50,080
Xiaohe has appeared.

565
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:52,120
Someone saw her
buying cigarettes at Nanhu Market.

566
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,800
They even found
bus tickets in her pockets.

567
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,520
Nanhu Market.

568
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,640
Bus tickets.

569
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:57,880
And cigarettes too?

570
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,480
Check all bus stations
that serve Nanhu Market.

571
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,440
Okay.

572
00:37:05,520 --> 00:37:06,960
NANHU MARKET
